data.description: Beautiful and bright home sitting on spacious corner lot in the peaceful Huntington Forest neighborhood with NO HOA! Home welcomes you in off of covered front porch into the formal entryway. Entire main level is open with tons of natural light. Fully carpeted living space with gas fireplace leads straight into dining area or additional family space. Large kitchen with tons of counterspace and storage off to the side. Kitchen island doubles as a breakfast bar for 2 plus eating nook for more space. Upstairs huge primary bedroom suite with vaulted ceilings plus en-suite with dual sinks, garden tub, stand up shower & walk-in closet. French doors lead to a 4th bedroom option or ideal home office space / nursery. 2 additional bedrooms plus full hall bath make this house perfect for hosting family and friends. New back deck overlooks huge flat yard with tons of opportunity to create your own entertainment oasis. Side-load 2 car garage & driving provide plenty of parking. A MUST SEE!
